    "overview_subtitle": "The Converse of the Pythagorean Theorem",
    "overview_description": "In this lesson, students explain a proof of the converse of the Pythagorean Theorem. They solve problems in context by applying the Pythagorean Theorem or its converse. Students then generate Pythagorean triples."
  },
